posting_body: ['Plymouth Square', 'RENT:', '$1700 - $1750 / MONTH', 'SIZE:', '1003 sq ft', 'BEDROOMS:', '2', 'BATHROOMS:', '2', 'LEASE TERMS:', '12-Month', 'show contact info', 'UNIT FEATURES:', '❖ Ceiling Fans In Select Units', '❖ Dining Room', '❖ Dishwasher', '❖ Fireplace In Select Units', '❖ Intercom/Call Box', '❖ Microwave', '❖ Patio/Balcony', '❖ Vaulted Ceiling In Select Units', '❖ Views', '❖ Washer/Dryer', "Plymouth Square's community room comes with a full kitchen and pool table which can be reserved for private events.", 'Other property amenities include our well-appointed fitness center, outdoor sundeck and barbecue area, and our indoor swimming pool and hot tub.', 'Our residents also enjoy the tennis court, sand volleyball court, and walking paths.', 'Nearby shopping and restaurants are an added convenience.', 'PROPERTY FEATURES:', '❖ Bike Storage', '❖ Courtyard', '❖ Elevator', '❖ Free Weights', '❖ No Smoking', '❖ Picnic Area', '❖ Recycling', '❖ Sauna', '❖ Spa/Hot Tub', '❖ Tennis Court', '❖ 24-Hour Fitness Center', '❖ 24-Hour Indoor Heated Pool', '❖ Barbecue/Grill Area', '❖ Controlled Access Building', '❖ Disposal Chutes', '❖ On-site Maintenance', '❖ On-site Management', '❖ Reservable Clubhouse', '❖ Volleyball Court', '❖ Weight Machines', 'PET POLICY:', 'Cats Allowed: 2 allowed, One time Fee $200.00, Rent $25.00, Deposit $200.00.', 'Pet 2: Non-refundable Fee $100, Deposit $100 and Rent $15', 'VISIT OR CALL US TODAY!', '15300 N 37th Ave', 'Plymouth, MN 55446', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'A4A243ACCD9D41']
